# CS488 A2
> Mingze Xu, #20806115
## Compilation
The compiation steps is as follows:
```{bash}
$ cd A2
$ premake4 gmake
$ make
$ ./A2
```
The dev program has been run on the local virtual machine

## Manual
- Clipping to near and far plane is done before projection in 3D space, and all
other clippings are done after homogenization in 2D space.
- Model scaler can be negative, where the model will be streched in the opposite direction
- LookFrom and LookAt are initialized as if we were observing inside the screen
- Visitor pattern is used to apply different transformations to different objects (cube and gnomons)
